 to look for specific things based on your preferences or you can choose to ignore criticism.","The third section is the Paper Wizard, which helps with style. With this section you can create MLA, APA, Turabian or Chicago style term papers, thesis, dissertations or APA journal articles. This section also helps with creating appendices, forewords, tables and assists with research by providing a quick link to Google Scholar and other resources and databases.","The last section is the Citation Wizard, which helps you cite sources correctly. With this tool you select either MLA or APA style, and then simply enter the required information into a generator and it automatically generates the citations in the selected format.","Wizards 4 Students has an extensive built in help system and easy to understand instructions. We found this program extremely useful, but outdated, for example this software will work with OS’s as old as Windows 98 and Word 97. However, if you are trying to write your papers on an old system, this will work for you, unlike many of the newer programs, which have more advanced system requirements. This program is not Mac compatible.","If you are a student and need help organizing and writing a paper this is a helpful program; however, if you have a newer computer Microsoft Student costs on a bit more but offers writing tools and much more."]},"id":"83c350dc-9fba-4ee0-9f4f-46c39f4f768f","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_1185","url":"/wizards-4-students-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"aaron-mccarter","url":"/author/aaron-mccarter","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Aaron McCarter","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"EMPGWr9T6iJCifmMZAJCYY","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","datePublished":"2018-05-24T19:02:44Z","name":"Wizards 4 Students","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from viewing as part 